    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Handle missing values\n",
        "for col in ['Country', 'Director', 'Cast', 'Rating']:\n",
        "    netflix[col] = netflix[col].fillna('Unknown')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Convert Release_Date to datetime\n",
        "netflix['Release_Date'] = pd.to_datetime(netflix['Release_Date'], errors='coerce')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Extract year and month for trend analysis\n",
        "netflix['Year_Added'] = netflix['Release_Date'].dt.year\n",
        "netflix['Month_Added'] = netflix['Release_Date'].dt.month\n",
        "\n"

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Extract main genre from the 'Type' column\n",
        "netflix['Main_Genre'] = netflix['Type'].str.split(',').str[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Extract year from Release_Date\n",
        "netflix['Year'] = pd.to_datetime(netflix['Release_Date'], errors='coerce').dt.year\n",
        "\n",
        "# Select top 5 popular genres\n",
        "popular_genres = netflix['Main_Genre'].value_counts().head(5).index\n",
        "\n",
        "# Prepare trend data\n",
        "genre_trends = netflix[netflix['Main_Genre'].isin(popular_genres)] \\\n",
        "                .groupby(['Year','Main_Genre']).size().reset_index(name='Count')\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plot trend line\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n",
        "sns.lineplot(data=genre_trends, x='Year', y='Count', hue='Main_Genre', marker=\"o\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"Trend of Popular Genres Over Time\")\n",
        "plt.xlabel(\"Year\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Number of Titles\")\n",
        "plt.legend(title=\"Genre\")\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
